'''Red Cabbage''' is a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Red Cabbage Seeds]] after 9 days. The seeds are available starting in Year 2. There is a small chance of buying Red Cabbage or Red Cabbage Seeds from the [[Traveling Cart]].

