==Tailoring==
Red Cabbage can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Tank Top]]. 
*Male Version: [[File:Shirt129.png|24px]]
*Female Version: [[File:Shirt130.png|24px]]

It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*Red Cabbage may be randomly requested in [[Summer]] (year 2+) at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|780}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

